%F A086866 For n>1, a(n) = (n^2 + 9*n - 2)*2^(n-4). - _Ralf Stephan_, May 10 2004
%F A086866 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, Mar 18 2026: (Start)
%F A086866 G.f.: x^2*(5 - 13*x + 8*x^2)/(1 - 2*x)^3.
%F A086866 E.g.f.: (exp(2*x)*(2*x^2 + 10*x - 1) + 1 - 8*x)/8.
%F A086866 a(n) = 6*a(n-1) - 12*a(n-2) + 8*a(n-3) for n > 4. (End)
